Leading sports & digital entertainment company, BetKing, has delighted two of its customers with brand new SUVs as part of its just-concluded AFKON campaign. The campaign, tagged #ThatAFKONFeeling was launched in January as part of the company’s efforts to celebrate African football and reward BetKing customers during this year’s edition of the African Cup of Nations (AFCON). The glamorous car presentation ceremony which took place at Ikoyi, Lagos on 13th February 2022 had key stakeholders in attendance including Nigerian football legend and BetKing Brand Ambassador, J.J. Okocha, BetKing and KingMakers executives, and media. The cars were presented to the winners – Joseph Ezugwu from Anambra State and Ugochukwu Nwagbo from Edo State by JJ Okocha and Oladipo Olasope, Chief Financial Officer, Kingmakers. Speaking at the event, Oludare Kafar, Head, BTL Marketing, Kingmakers, said, “It’s been an exciting past few weeks and we are glad to wrap up the AFKON campaign in grand style as we reward 2 of some of our winners with brand new car prizes. At BetKing, we are deeply committed to celebrating African football and rewarding our customers, hence, we look forward to future initiatives such as this.” “As you can see, for this campaign, there is still one more brand new SUV available to be won, and we are on the search for the winner. We urge our customers to partake in this very exciting promo to stand a chance to win the third JAC SUV.”, Oludare added. In addition to the cars, the 3 winners will also be receiving exclusive BetKing jackets officially signed by J.J. Okocha. One of the winners of the cars, Joseph Ezugwu, said, “I am beyond excited and very grateful to BetKing for my brand new SUV. Today, I truly feel like a King and I owe that to BetKing.” BetKing remains committed to shaping the standards for sports entertainment in Africa by providing trusted and quality services to customers. About BetKing BetKing is a sports betting and digital entertainment company offering online services in Nigeria, Kenya, Ethiopia, and Ghana, as well as agency services in Nigeria. Among the offerings of the company’s services are sports betting, not restricted to football, hockey, cricket, tennis, basketball, and more, customized state-of-the-art virtual games including the exclusive Kings’ League and Colour-Colour. BetKing also offers agency opportunities for individuals who will come to be called Kingmakers once they sign up to deliver offline betting services to customers. BetKing is a product of SV Gaming Limited and the birth of the brand was initiated by evolution in strategy and the objective to offer more value to customers. BetKing is currently licensed to operate across Nigeria, with licenses from the National Lottery Regulatory Commission, Lagos State Lotteries and Gaming Authority, amongst others. For more information about BetKing, please visit: betking.com  <img class="alignnone wp-image-663042" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BetKing-AFKON-SUVs.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BetKing-AFKON-SUVs.jpg 2558w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BetKing-AFKON-SUVs-300x200.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BetKing-AFKON-SUVs-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BetKing-AFKON-SUVs-768x512.jpg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BetKing-AFKON-SUVs-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BetKing-AFKON-SUVs-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BetKing-AFKON-SUVs-24x16.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BetKing-AFKON-SUVs-36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BetKing-AFKON-SUVs-48x32.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /> <img clas